      <title>墨西哥当局搜寻失踪的澳大利亚和美国游客</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/mexican-authorities-search-missing-australian-us-tourists-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥当局周四表示，他们正在海上和陆地上搜寻两名澳大利亚人和一名据报在该国暴力最严重的州之一下加利福尼亚州失踪的美国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/mexican-authorities-search-missing-australian-us-tourists-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元有望创一年多以来最佳单周表现；美元等待美国就业数据</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-poised-best-week-over-year-dollar-waits-us-jobs-data-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，日元创下一年多以来的最佳单周表现，得益于本周东京方面疑似干预，日元脱离了 34 年来的低点，这也导致美元普遍处于劣势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-poised-best-week-over-year-dollar-waits-us-jobs-data-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透调查显示澳洲联储5月维持利率不变，年底仅降息一次</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/rba-hold-rates-may-only-cut-once-by-end-year-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社对经济学家的调查显示，澳大利亚央行将在周二连续第四次召开会议，将关键政策利率维持在 4.35%，至少持续到 9 月底，经济学家预计今年只会降息一次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/rba-hold-rates-may-only-cut-once-by-end-year-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:16:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着大宗商品暴利的消失，麦格理的年度利润大幅下滑；股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australias-macquarie-posts-32-fall-full-year-profit-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚顶级投资银行麦格理表示，由于能源市场的稳定对其大宗商品交易部门造成重创，且出售绿色能源资产的利润减少，其年度利润下降了三分之一，为 15 年来的最大降幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australias-macquarie-posts-32-fall-full-year-profit-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:18:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰外长称中国关系复杂</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-foreign-minister-calls-china-relationship-complex-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰外交部长周五称该国与中国的关系“复杂”，并指出台湾海峡两岸的强硬言论、香港的侵犯人权行为以及“加强对太平洋安全领域的参与”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-foreign-minister-calls-china-relationship-complex-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:57:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
