    <item>
      <title>MP Materials 报告称，由于稀土价格疲软，第一季度亏损超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/mp-materials-report-wider-than-expected-q1-loss-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[稀土矿商 MP Materials 周四报告称，由于精矿销量下降和战略矿物价格疲软，第一季度亏损超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/mp-materials-report-wider-than-expected-q1-loss-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:23:26 GMT</pubDate>
